thread.title: Maureen Lees
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Maureen Lees

author: Maureen Lees
title: Maureen Lees
text: Product of Ink Cartridges for my printer were extremely well priced, despatched quickly with E-mail notification of the progress, and delivered within a couple of days by courier. The retail stores did not have the colour cartridge I needed. So I ended up with 2 black and 2 colour cartridges for the same price I would normally pay for just the 2. Now have extra stock on hand. Thank you Ink Station, as my printer was completely out of ink.
